<br>
I've read many many fantasy novels and my favourites include the Riftwar Saga by Raymond E Feist, and the Darkelf Trilogy by R A Salvatore.<br>
<br>
I'm looking for something similar to those..any ideas?  There seems to be many new series in the book stores and I don't know which to choose <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I found David Eddings novels to be a tad childish, but entertaining nonetheless.<br>
<br>
Wheel of Time was good for a while, but I feel its become drawn out and boring 8(<br>
